mployers alumni referrals etc to learn about possible positions be patient the average job search takes anywhere from three to six months of active job seeking so don t get discouraged if you are still looking for the right job late in spring quarter back to top for undergraduates up career paths for phd students groups career development center printer friendly version calendar schedule an appointment graphic calendar pages schedule an appointment with a career counselor quick links calendar career fair schedule career planning handbook career library vault guided career path facebook linkedin what is the cdc copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
